Source: pgclone
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/valehdba/pgclone

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pgclone
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pgclone
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Clone PostgreSQL databases, schemas, and tables across environments
  pgclone clones databases, schemas, tables, and functions directly from SQL,
  including asynchronous and selective copy workflows.
